# Monorepo Layout

```
.
├── apps/
│   ├── backend/       ← NestJS backend
│   └── client/        ← TanStack Start frontend
├── packages/
│   ├── rbac/          ← Better Auth RBAC plugin (workspace package)
│   ├── templates/     ← React Email templates
│   ├── tsconfig/      ← shared tsconfig presets
│   └── ui/            ← shadcn-based UI component library (workspace package)
├── package.json       ← root workspace config
├── bunfig.toml        ← isolated linker
├── vite.config.ts     ← Vite+ task runner & code review tasks
├── tsconfig.json      ← root TS config
├── commitlint.config.ts
├── .lintstagedrc.json
├── .release-it.json
├── knip.config.ts     ← dead code detection
└── AGENTS.md
```

## Quick Commands

| What                    | Command                              |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| Install deps            | `vp install`                         |
| Run all checks          | `vp check` (or `vp check --fix`)     |
| Run all tests           | `vp run -r test`                     |
| Run a single test file  | `vitest run <path>` from package dir |
| Build all packages/apps | `vp run -r build`                    |
| Dev mode                | `vp run`                             |
| Dead code / unused deps | `knip`                               |
| Release                 | `release-it`                         |

## Package Manager

Bun with isolated linker (`bunfig.toml`). **Never use npm or pnpm.**

## Backend (apps/backend)

- **Runtime**: NestJS v12, TypeScript 7 (`@typescript/native-preview`), CJS output.
- **Email**: React Email templates in `packages/templates/`, compiled at build time.
- **TypeScript**: Uses native path rewriting via TS7 — no `tsconfig-paths` or `tsc-alias`.
- **Path aliases**: `@/*`, `@module/*`, `@config/*`, `@lib/*`, `@constant/*` map to `./src/*` variants.
- **Backend boilerplate**: Nest helpers live as local source under `apps/backend/src` (middleware, guards, decorators, abstract classes, package modules). Do not depend on `@[[ project_name ]]/nest`.
- **Auth**: Better Auth with MikroORM adapter. RBAC permissions plugin lives in `packages/rbac/` (workspace package `@[[ project_name ]]/rbac`).
- **DB**: MikroORM with PostgreSQL driver.

## Client (apps/client)

- **Runtime**: TanStack Start (React 19, SSR), Vite, TypeScript.
- **UI**: `@[[ project_name ]]/ui` (workspace package) for components, Tailwind CSS v4 for styling.
- **Auth**: Better Auth client with `@[[ project_name ]]/rbac` plugin, session middleware.
- **Data fetching**: TanStack Query v5 with SSR query integration.
- **Routing**: TanStack Router with file-based routes (`app/` directory), auto-generated route tree.
- **i18n**: Paraglide (inlang) with URL-based locale strategy.
- **API client**: `@[[ project_name ]]/sdk` (workspace package) — generated by the backend at startup. Stub types exist for compilation; run the backend to regenerate.

## SDK (packages/sdk)

- **Source**: OpenAPI-generated TypeScript axios client.
- **Generation**: Run the backend in development mode — it generates `openapi.json` from NestJS + Better Auth specs, then produces client code into `packages/sdk/src/`.
- **Stub**: The skeleton provides stub `Configuration` and `User` types so the client compiles before the first generation.
